# Verification of Award and Ranking

## Overview
This document serves as verification for the award and ranking achieved in the **2024 China Undergraduate Mathematical Contest in Modeling (CUMCM)** (2024年全国大学生数学建模竞赛).

* **Award Received:** National Second Prize (Undergraduate Group)
* **Ranking:** Top **2.53%** among all participating undergraduate teams.

## Competition Statistics & Ranking Calculation
According to the official statistics released by the CUMCM organizing committee, the competition scale and award distribution for the Undergraduate Group are as follows:

* **Total Undergraduate Teams:** 59,278
* **National First Prize:** 296 teams
* **National Second Prize:** 1,204 teams

**Ranking Logic:**
Our team received the National Second Prize. Based on the total number of participants, the top percentage is calculated as:
\[
\frac{296 (\text{1st Prize}) + 1204 (\text{2nd Prize})}{59,278 (\text{Total Teams})} \approx \mathbf{2.53\%}
\]

**Official Sources:**
* [Competition Statistics Announcement](https://www.mcm.edu.cn/html_cn/node/993811071382f502658d2b50953eb68d.html)
* [Participation Data (PDF)](https://www.mcm.edu.cn/upload_cn/node/739/Ym9QisLn125c5f8a7cd596802bfeaaf3fc0220ec.pdf)

---

## Verification Methods

You can verify the award authenticity using either of the following two methods:

### Method 1: Official Award List (PDF)
The award information is listed in the official document published on the CUMCM website.

* **Source URL:** [CUMCM Award Notification](https://www.mcm.edu.cn/html_cn/node/3aa4e9fc4c5a755da53b343660cdaf59.html)
* **Direct PDF Link:** [Undergraduate Group Award List](https://www.mcm.edu.cn/upload_cn/node/733/4rFKQqyT96ee1e63dd8d2408e56df8b2ec172125.pdf)

**How to find us:**
1.  Open the PDF link above.
2.  Navigate to **Page 11**.
3.  Look for **Row 286**.
4.  You will find the team information:
    * **Name:** 鲁任文
    * **University:** 哈尔滨工程大学

*(Note: The award summary is on Page 1 for First Prize and Page 6 for Second Prize).*

### Method 2: Ministry of Education Query System
You can also verify the award through the "China University Students Online" (中国大学生在线) award query system provided by the Ministry of Education.

* **Query URL:** [https://dxs.moe.gov.cn/zx/awards/index.shtml](https://dxs.moe.gov.cn/zx/awards/index.shtml)

**Input Instructions:**
Please input the following information into the query form (from top to bottom):

1.  **Name (姓名):** `鲁任文`
2.  **School (学校):** `哈尔滨工程大学`
3.  **Competition (赛事名称):** Select `全国大学生数学建模竞赛`
4.  **Year (获奖年份):** Select `2024`

After clicking query, the system will display the verified National Second Prize certificate information.
